t: "Then in the footsteps of these ňĻprophetsňļ, We sent Our messengers, and ňĻafter themňļ We sent Jesus, son of Mary, and granted him the Gospel, and instilled compassion and mercy into the hearts of his followers. As for monasticism, they made it up‚ÄĒWe never ordained it for them‚ÄĒonly seeking to please God, yet they did not ňĻevenňļ observe it strictly. So We rewarded those of them who were faithful. But most of them are rebellious"